<br>
The game is 3/4 view, which is not as good as EQ's first person, but the view is a lot better than BG2.<br>
<br>
What intriques me is the use of near-exact Dungeons and Dragons 3rd edition rules, meaning that monks are back.  Quivering Palm and all the other monk goodies are implemented too...even the Grandmaster of Flowers title  heheh.<br>
<br>
Anyone waiting for this?  Expect it to be good or to fail?<br>
